    <title><custom ref="synthesis-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Display a number line folded into fourths and a fraction strip of fourths.</li>
      <li>
        <q>¿En qué se pareció partir estas rectas numéricas a partir nuestras tiras de fracciones?</q>  (The number lines were folded just like the strips were, but instead of a rectangle it’s just a line. We labeled the location of the unit fractions at the end of the first part on each number line instead of the space.)
      </li>
    </ul>
